sources.name: SourceDataset_avz
sources.script:
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> SourceDataset_avz

typeProperties.script:
section Section1;
shared SourceDataset_avz = let
  AdfDoc = Sql.Database("cdmbricks.database.windows.net", "WWI"),
  InputTable = AdfDoc{[Schema = "Application", Item = "Cities"]}[Data]
in
  InputTable;
shared UserQuery = let
  Source = SourceDataset_avz,
  #"Removed columns" = Table.RemoveColumns(Source, {"StateProvinceID"})
in
  #"Removed columns";
